Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:33.63,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}予測できないトキメキ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:37.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's TRUE FOOL LOVE! Hold me tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:39.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}勇気を出してよマイダーリン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:44.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬉しい楽しいばっかじゃない　自分次第
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ONCE MORE SMILE, TWICE MORE CHIME
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:49.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こっち向いてよダーリン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:58.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}わたしの純愛に気づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:37.74,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之多少的喜歡才算是戀愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.83,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慫是罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:52.55,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}腦力激盪滴滴答答 選一種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.01,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雲隙中一陣細雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.05,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不亞至高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:01.60,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少女心它陰晴不定 可愛且無敵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:04.14,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像雜亂無章的鐘聲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:11.40,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之多少的喜歡才算是戀愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:15.11,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱著我直到我想睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:20.66,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像是科幻片般的白日夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:23.70,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}親吻我 打破劇中沉默吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.12,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}優柔寡斷也好 抱緊我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.79,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胸口悶得難受好難受好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:33.63,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心動無法預測
Comment: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:37.09,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's TRUE FOOL LOVE! Hold me tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:39.38,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼓起勇氣來呀 My darling
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:44.01,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不止於歡樂和欣喜 都取決於我們自己
Comment: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.31,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ONCE MORE SMILE, TWICE MORE CHIME
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:49.56,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}轉過來看著我吧 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:58.95,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}注意到我純粹的愛呀
